{"tid":533902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【天眼影晒】男子懷巨款買Bitcoin 遭3口罩賊搶$140萬","createTime":"2018-01-19T09:34:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T13:41:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"090f05af3e88559b6e34dd9fed796af51aaa1795","tid":533902,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:34:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180119/large/1516340828_0a58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180119%2Flarge%2F1516340828_0a58.jpg&h=456c77e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名比特幣交易商，昨晚在北角英皇道遭3名南亞裔賊人，當街搶走140萬港元。附近一間生果檔的閉路電視，拍攝到歹徒逃走時的情況。片中可見，3名戴有口罩的賊匪快步跑過，當中一人右手攬著相信是事主載滿現金的電腦袋。其間多名途人目擊事件，指著匪徒。約40秒後，事主右手拿著電腦袋被扯斷的孭帶，左手拿手機，一邊報警一邊追捕。<br />\n<br />\n事發於昨晚10時許，34歲姓李男子，相約比特幣賣家，在英皇道麥當勞會面，其間對方聲稱「唔識路」，著事主出外相接。當事主途至英皇道與北角道交界的恆生銀行對開。突遭3名戴口罩的南亞賊箍頸，搶去放有約140萬元現金的黑色電腦袋，並沿北角道北行、向渣華道方向逃去。<br />\n<br />\n據現場消息稱，事主尾隨追趕期間意外仆倒，手腳受傷，亦有多名途人協助報警。事主追到50米外的北角道與春秧街交界的生果檔，似乎失去賊人蹤影，一臉焦急，唯有向職員追問賊人逃跑方向，可惜他最終未能截停賊匪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180119/57727060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57727060&d=O%2FDIUHGNus3%2BZXxg%2BPUTdUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=7d9888a5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180119%2F57727060&h=d3af6639\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180119/57727060</a>"},{"pid":"319c87476b2382d5b655eeea4617706c7c902740","tid":533902,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:35:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇啦冇啦"},{"pid":"a9527cafe52f17f104863c375c39fbf836c799da","tid":533902,"uid":33868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:36:28.000Z","msg":"現金仲危險過Crypto"},{"pid":"7616c1a3baa21db8fda865dc98fa0f9b1d668eb4","tid":533902,"uid":22736,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"以前就省港奇兵依就南亞賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d7096f368ed9bf329caeec18aa9a3766fbdce1c","tid":533902,"uid":164770,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:57:33.000Z","msg":"好明顯個賣家派人"},{"pid":"829f98cbed6db5ac1f8958e66ab82217cc3468f3","tid":533902,"uid":51343,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"光天化日&hellip;"},{"pid":"78632629516904af722e00d859d7c7643c6d40e4","tid":533902,"uid":19552,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:01:20.000Z","msg":"我地南亞囝囝先係香港新主人"},{"pid":"ca5c4cf108922ea3ea7ef29c30288d30b9eab324","tid":533902,"uid":1767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:02:11.000Z","msg":"一定有預謀 無啦啦點會揀中佢黎搶<br />\n有機會自己人做"},{"pid":"7ae19ee42f040a7be93e108e3cbabf8868d2bb69","tid":533902,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:03:15.000Z","msg":"好彩咁耐以黎都無出事"},{"pid":"b205e560a00da9dafc1303782a120a00c2267679","tid":533902,"uid":35995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:04:52.000Z","msg":"傻仔sosad 擺明呃9你拎現金出黎"},{"pid":"f6256057e0f941b521615956a709d627c74d3562","tid":533902,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港無乜方法買bitcoin?"},{"pid":"af7335ecf2b3ae837d9c6ecc9655a3c3ff5a891e","tid":533902,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔想比人食手續費<br />\n抵死"},{"pid":"8c441b956dad2f0a3cb8c1035ce8d8559cadd957","tid":533902,"uid":28619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited